title: Fatal Instinct (1993) Comedy
description:
A spoof of the late 80s and early 90s suspense thrillers and murder mysteries, 
including Basic Instinct, Sleeping With The Enemy, Cape Fear and others. A 
cop/attorney (yes he's both) is seduced by a woman while his wife is having an 
affair with a mechanic. Lots of other sublots and visual gags in the style of 
Naked Gun.
